## Overview

Markdown is the language that I use to write documentation so I will be writing a list for its syntax. You can find dozen of Md syntax articles after a quick search on the internet but mine will be specific to my style of writing. I'll also add quite a bit of html and javascript syntax. I'll post it as I use it on the daily basis in my work.

### Heading

